ormat":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019iz al-Tamimi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich deeds are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah alone, then jihad, and then a blessed pilgrimage are better than all other deeds like the distance between the rising of the sun and its setting.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/best-jihad-women-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6565,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Best jihad for women is Hajj pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not attend the military expeditions and fight in jihad alongside you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo, rather the best and most beautiful jihad for you is the Hajj, a blessed pilgrimage.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1861\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18530,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/15\/hajj-umrah-cut-shave-head\/","url_meta":{"origin":6565,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Recommendation to shave head, permission to cut only","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: At the end of the Hajj pilgrimage, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon those who shaved their heads.\u201d They said, \u201cAnd those who cut their hair short, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cO Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/ramadan-umrah-hajj\/","url_meta":{"origin":6565,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: &#8216;Umrah in Ramadan equal to Hajj","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the 'Umrah pilgrimage during Ramadan is equal to Hajj.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1782, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1256 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32857,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/d